  <div id="text-content_DD4EFCF3-9997-4C26-9194-2088F9ACCC1C" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Ensure the <strong>Report replies </strong>checkbox is selected [1].</p>
<p>To save discussion settings, click the <strong>Save Settings</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
